name: Gang Muscle #1532
description: There are 2222 pixel NFTs in Sui Gang. They are fully unique and randomized with tons of different traits! Each NFT makes it possible to earn $GANG tokens. The rarer your NFT, the more tokens it brings. In addition to $GANG tokens, NFT holders get rewarded with SUI coins, as 100% of the royalty will be distributed monthly among them.
